'''設計博物館'''（{{lang-fi|Designmuseo}}，{{lang-sv|Designmuseet}}）是位於[[芬蘭|芬蘭]]首都[[赫爾辛基|赫爾辛基]]的一座博物館，專門展示芬蘭國內外有關設計的展覽品，包括工業設計、時裝和平面設計。設計博物館成立於1873年，是世界上歷史最早的有關视觉設計的博物館之一。<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://theculturetrip.com/europe/finland/articles/the-top-7-things-to-do-in-helsinki-s-design-district/|title = The Top 7 Things To Do in Helsinki's Design District|accessdate = 2016-02-28|author = |date = 2015-11-14|publisher = The Culture Trip|archive-date = 2021-03-06|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210306165621/https://theculturetrip.com/europe/finland/articles/the-top-7-things-to-do-in-helsinki-s-design-district/|dead-url = no}}</ref>博物館所在建築曾經是一座學校。博物馆收藏有超过75,000件设计物品、45,000幅画作以及125,000幅照片。<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.designmuseum.fi/en/collections/|title = The museum's collections|accessdate = 2016-02-28|author = |date = |publisher = Design Museum|archive-date = 2020-12-02|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201202221518/https://www.designmuseum.fi/en/collections/|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.finnishdesign.com/museums-and-factories/design-museum-finland|title = Design Museum Finland|accessdate = 2016-02-28|author = |date = |publisher = Finnish Design|archive-date = 2016-09-14|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160914175834/http://www.finnishdesign.com/museums-and-factories/design-museum-finland|dead-url = no}}</ref>

